casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
LOWERY S240615 Supreme Court of California. JANUARY 23, 2019

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger and Groban JJ.

The above-captioned matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Sixth Appellate District, with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the cause in light of People v. Franco (2018) 6 Cal.5th 433, 240 Cal.Rptr.3d 766, 430 P.3d 1233. ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
